      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 3987,
        "name": "静谧之曲",
        "desc": "<p>外观奇异如海中生物的长弓，弦振之时似乎毫无声音。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/16/47826599/32cb6067727cbf3e630e0bcba488d8b5_1328977054782256040.png",
